QUALIFICATION: Panagra curtaria Walker, 1863 is a junior primary homonym of Panagra curtaria Guenée, 1857. No holotype could be found in BMNH and it is possible that Walker was redescribing Guenée's species but the reference to Guenée was omitted. The species is unidentifiable from Walker's description but is included here because of the probability that Walker was redescribing Guenée's species
